-1.title: Casefiles: Unknown
-1.plot: Casefiles: Unknown tells the stories of real life paranormal encounters supported by riveting footage and evidence collected by everyday people. You will hear real stories that attempt to make sense of the unexplained occurrences that they have encountered in their daily lives. From souls leaving their bodies to alien implantation, Casefiles: Unknown aims to make sense of the seemingly inexplicable paranormal experiences that unfold in our world everyday.
